  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Start preparing the potatoes</strong></p>\n<p>Boil a kettle.</p>\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces.</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook the potatoes</strong></p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot of<strong> boiled water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat. Bring to the boil and cook for 10-15 minutes or until fork-tender.</p>\n<p>Once cooked, drain and return them to the pot.</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Prepare the feta skordalia</strong></p>\n<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely grate the<strong> garlic</strong>.</p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>lemon<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half.</p>\n<p>Chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks (keep the chopped leaves and stalks separate!) and set aside for later.</p>\n<p>Mash the <strong>feta</strong> with a fork until smooth. Re-boil a kettle.</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook the diced chorizo </strong></p>\n<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat.</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced chorizo</strong> and cook for 5-6 minutes or until starting to crisp.</p>\n<p>Once starting to crisp, transfer the <strong>chorizo</strong> and<strong> oil</strong> to a plate and reserve for later.</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Finish making the feta skordalia</strong></p>\n<p>Return the <strong>drained potatoes</strong> to a low heat.</p>\n<p>Add 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span> <strong>milk</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil, </strong>the<strong> grated garlic </strong>(Don't like raw garlic? Go easy!) and <strong>mashed feta </strong>and mash until smooth.</p>\n<p>Once done, cover to keep warm and set aside until serving – this is your <strong>feta skordalia</strong>.</p>\n<p> </p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook your Tenderstem and prep the scallops</strong></p>\n<p>Pour the<strong> boiled water</strong> into a pot over a high heat. Add a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>.</p>\n<p>Once the water comes to the boil, add the <strong>Tenderstem broccoli</strong> and cook for 4 minutes or until tender, then drain.</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, pat the <strong>scallops</strong> dry with kitchen roll.</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook your scallops</strong></p>\n<p>Return the pan to a high heat. Once very hot, add the <strong>scallops</strong> and cook for 1-2 minutes on one side until golden.</p>\n<p>Once brown, flip the <strong>scallops</strong> and add the<strong> Chinese rice wine</strong>, <strong>capers</strong>, <strong>reserved chorizo </strong>and <strong>oil</strong> and cook for 1-2 minutes.</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>juice</strong> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and cook for 1 minute or until the <strong>scallops</strong> are cooked through.<span class=\"text-highlight\"> This is your <strong>scallops &amp; chorizo</strong>.</span></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/pan-fried-scallops-with-chorizo-feta-skordalia-and-tenderstem/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Serve up!</strong></p>\n<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges.</p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>scallops &amp; chorizo</strong> over the <strong>feta skordalia</strong> with the <strong>drained Tenderstem</strong> to the side.</p>\n<p>Sprinkle over the <strong>flaked almonds</strong> and garnish with a wedge of<strong> lemon</strong>.</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
